insert into oglasi (id, naziv, kat_id, pos_id, url, opis_posla, rok_prijave) values (1662, 'Human Resources Specialist (m/f)', 12, 1429, 'https://www.moj-posao.net/Posao/506130/Human-Resources-Specialist-mf/', 'Opis posla
					Responsibilities

Human Resources Specialist is responsible for activities of the whole selection and recruitment process within the Optimapharm group and is actively involved as support in all human resources related processes within the Company:

- Actively participating and managing the selection process of new employees – preparing employment ads, keeping records of received applications, interviews and tests, contacting candidates, organizing the selection process, support in resume selection and CV database search, identifying new selection channels and contacts with potential candidates for employment

- Coordinating the whole onboarding process of new employees 

- Actively participating and giving support in organizing trainings and education for company’s employees, keeping necessary records and preparing necessary documentation, collecting offers from training/courses suppliers and contacting them when needed

- Providing support in employee performance appraisal activities, employee rewarding systems and employee development processes, preparing required analysis and reports: preparing employee benefit analysis, collecting data and analyzing existing benefits when needed.

- Participating in the processes of internal communication development, preparation of internal communication content (information e-mails to employees etc.), organizing internal events and actively contributing to the development of quality and open relationships within the company

- Implementation of Employee Satisfaction Survey, interpretation of results, preparation of presentations and action plans

- Supporting the development of internal human resources management processes and involvement in identifying necessities for improvements 

- Actively participating in creation of content for Company’s social networks profiles in collaboration with Business Development Department (LinkedIn, Facebook, Twitter....)

- Assisting Human Resources Manager in other activities within the Department', to_date('03.02.2021.', 'dd.mm.yyyy.'));
